questions.title: 不是因为这条裙子不好看，而是因为我不喜欢短的裙子。
questions.answer: Not that this skirt is not beautiful, but that I don't like short skirt.

questions.title: 不是你不帅气，而是因为你今天的穿着不适合你。
questions.answer: Not that you are not handsome, but that your dress doesn't suit youtoday.

questions.title: 不是我不想爱你，而是我没有力气爱你。
questions.answer: Not that I don't want to love you, but that I lack the strength to loveyou.

questions.title: 不是我逃避借你钱，而是我没有足够的钱。
questions.answer: Not that I escape to lend you money, but that I don't have enough.

title: ——难道你不喜欢贝克汉姆？
——不是不喜欢他，而是不了解他。

answer.en: Not that I don't like him, but that I don't know anything about him.

title: ——我好奇他为什么要放弃那么好的工作？
——他放弃并不是因为不喜欢这份工作，而是因为无法胜任。

answer.en: I wonder why he gave such a decent job up.
He gave up the work, not that he disliked it, but that he was unequal toit.
